<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 300px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      background-color: #111;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;

      &:hover {
        text-decoration: none !important;
      }
    }

    a:hover {
      background-color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white !important;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <img loading="lazy" src="/images/icons/image.png" alt="3D 404 Illustration" width="30">
  <h1 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight:bold;">404 - Oops! Maaf halaman tidak ditemukan</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 14px;">Halaman yang anda cari kemungkinan tidak ada<br/>atau sudah mengalami perubahan</p>
  <a href="/" style="padding:8px 14px;font-size:12px;">Kembali ke Halaman Utama</a>
</body>
</html>
